  "implementation_instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Ensure the application renders in Dark Mode with #0F0F12 as the main safe-area background.",
    "The avatar ring row must map to user's friends with active states showing a yellow (#FFD700) ring border.",
    "For rendering Pixel Art in React Native/Expo, use resizeMode='contain' on <Image> tags. On Web platforms, apply style: { imageRendering: 'pixelated' } to preserve the crisp 8-bit edges and avoid blurry anti-aliasing.",
    "Construct the room as a solid colored container (backgroundColor: #E8D4A6) filling the remaining flex space, bordered with 24px top radiuses.",
    "All floating UI like 'Chat Input' and 'Tab Pills' must be layered absolute over the room and have fully rounded corners (borderRadius: 9999).",
    "Interactive elements MUST have a data-testid attribute in kebab-case."
  ]
